          </p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;">
          This standoff occurred as the US and Philippines held their largest joint military drills, with Japan participating for the first time. Under President Trump, the US has promised strong support for Manila. Top officials aim to deter China‚Äôs aggression. This incident shows the growing risks of a larger conflict in the strategic South China Sea.</p>
